S Power FM|Power Time]]'' within the two weeks of promotions.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/109/0004188553|title=\uac15\ub2e4\ub2c8\uc5d8, \uc74c\ubc29 3\uad00\uc655 \ub2ec\uc131..7\uc77c '\uc1fc\ucc54' \ub05d\uc73c\ub85c '2U' \ud65c\ub3d9 \ub05d [\uacf5\uc2dd]|date=April 6, 2020|website=OSEN|access-date=April 6, 2020|language=ko}}</ref>\n\n==Commercial performance==\n''Cyan'' surpassed 200,000 cumulative physical album sales within three days of release, marking the highest cumulative sales in 2020 by a soloist at the time. It ranked first in 9 countries' [[iTunes]] charts and first in 12 countries' K-pop album charts upon release. ''Cyan'' also achieved a [[Gaon Music Chart|Gaon]] triple crown by topping the album, download, and BGM weekly charts.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/109/0004185839|title=\uac15\ub2e4\ub2c8\uc5d8, \uc0c1\ud07c\u00b7\uccad\ub7c9 '\uc778\uac04 \uc774\uc628\uc74c\ub8cc' \ud0c4\uc0dd\u2026\uaf49 \ucc44\uc6b4 1\uc8fc \ucc28 \ud65c\ub3d9 \ub9c8\ubb34\ub9ac|date=March 30, 2020|website=OSEN|access-date=April 6, 2020|language=ko}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/109/0004188553|title=\uac15\ub2e4\ub2c8\uc5d8, \uc74c\ubc29 3\uad00\uc655 \ub2ec\uc131..7\uc77c '\uc1fc\ucc54' \ub05d\uc73c\ub85c '2U' \ud65c\ub3d9 \ub05d [\uacf5\uc2dd]|date=April 6, 2020|website=OSEN|access-date=April 6, 2020|language=ko}}</ref> \n\n==Track listing==\n'''Digital download/CD'''<ref>{{cite news |title=\uac15\ub2e4\ub2c8\uc5d8 \ubbf8\ub2c8 1\uc9d1 \ud0c0\uc774\ud2c0\uace1 \u20182U\u2019, \uc81c\ubaa9\ubd80\ud130 \ud1b5\ud1b5 \ud284\ub2e4 |url=https://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=609&aid=0000258592 |work=Newsen |date=March 17, 2020 |access-date=March 17, 2020|language=ko}}</ref>\n{{Track listing\n| total_length = 16:16\n| extra_column = Arrangement\n \n| title1 = Adulthood\n| lyrics1 = dwvn, Noday, Versachoi, Kang Daniel\n| music1 = Noday, dwvn, Versachoi\n| extra1 = Versac